`getNaturalSizeAndAlignment` for interface types calls `getSizeAndAlignment` with `NaturalLayoutRules`, which calls `calcSizeAndAlignment`. For `kIROp_InterfaceType`, this calls `getInterfaceAnyValueSize`, which... let me check what this returns.

